These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-1::.
City: new-york, marseilles
The people have 2 different jobs:  designer, social-worker
House: townhouse, colonial
The people use 2 different means of transport: bike, jet-ski
1. the person traveling to new-york is on the far right##1
2. the townhouse house is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
3. the designer is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2     |
| City       | marseilles       | new-york |
| Job         | social-worker | designer  |
| House       | colonial    | townhouse    |
| Transport   | jet-ski       | bike      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-2::.
2 different pets are kept: snake, hamster
The people have 2 different jobs:  entrepreneur, lawyer
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: poppy, daisy
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: snowboarding, surfing
1. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
2. the entrepreneur is on the far left##1
3. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |
| Pet      | hamster     | snake |
| Job           | entrepreneur | lawyer      |
| Flower   | daisy  | poppy      |
| Sport         | snowboarding | surfing     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, soy-milk
There 2 different types of food: apple, avocado
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: poppy, azalea
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, old-henry
1. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
2. the person drinking iced-tea is the old-henry-smoker##1
3. the person eating apple is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Beverage      | iced-tea | soy-milk  |
| Food          | apple    | avocado   |
| Flower   | azalea  | poppy   |
| Cigar     | old-henry     | havana |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-4::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: handball, snowboarding
There 2 different types of food: lemon, papaya
The people have 2 different jobs:  nurse, security-guard
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: adventure, western
1. the person watching adventure movies is on the far left##1
2. the nurse is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the person eating lemon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Sport      | handball       | snowboarding |
| Food          | papaya         | lemon    |
| Job           | security-guard | nurse    |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure           | western   |

