2 different games are played: domino, canasta
The people have 2 different hobbies: board-games, chess
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: funk, indie
1. the fan of indie is on the left of the person playing domino##1
2. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
3. the fan of indie is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |     2     |
| Beverage   | 7up         | coffee    |
| Game       | canasta     | domino  |
| Hobby      | board-games | chess     |
| Music-Genre        | indie     | funk |

