There 2 different types of food: nectarine, avocado
2 different pets are kept: mouse, rabbit
The people use 2 different means of transport: bus, van
1. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person eating nectarine##1
2. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person driving the van##1
3. the owner of the mouse is the person playing whist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |
| Game           | whist | bridge     |
| Food   | nectarine          | avocado |
| Pet           | mouse          | rabbit    |
| Transport     | van            | bus       |

 